  "2026-07-09T21:35:58.172Z",codex-foundation,Specialized agent started scoped production audit on 2026-07-09; pm-cli source and telemetry/observability configuration are out of scope.
  "2026-07-09T21:36:07.924Z",codex-foundation,"2026-07-09 scope checkpoint: inventorying GitHub reports, current PR branch, dependency versions, release automation, package activation, real-workspace behavior, and full-history privacy posture before implementation."
notes[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-09T21:35:58.172Z",codex-foundation,"Evidence will include exact commands, linked files/docs/tests, GitHub review disposition, package tarball verification, real workspace fixtures, and path-only sensitive-data scan summaries."
  "2026-07-09T21:36:08.275Z",codex-foundation,Toolchain baseline is global pm CLI 2026.7.9. Required package target is @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.7.9 and pm-changelog 2026.7.8 after registry verification. No telemetry/observability changes are authorized.
body: "Audit GitHub issues, PRs, checks, dependency/security reports, full history, package contents, and real preset apply/diff/export/validate workflows. Preserve unrelated work. Keep all presets consolidated in pm-presets with simple branding. Generate CHANGELOG.md and release notes with pm-changelog. Verify daily change-gated GitHub/npm/Bun release automation. Run Greptile before push, then bot review loops to green."
